---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-end pt-32 pb-20 px-[var(--spacing-margin-mobile)] md:px-[var(--spacing-margin-desktop)] max-w-[var(--spacing-container-max)] mx-auto">
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-[600px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
    <!-- Optional: Add a webgl canvas or background image here if needed -->
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 space-y-8">
    <p class="font-label-caps text-[length:var(--text-label-caps)] text-on-surface-variant uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
      EST. 2024 / DIGITAL AGENCY
    </p>
    
    <h1 class="font-display-lg-mobile md:font-display-lg text-[length:var(--text-display-lg-mobile)] md:text-[length:var(--text-display-lg)] text-primary max-w-5xl leading-none">
      LUNAWEB: ARQUITECTURA DIGITAL
    </h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 pt-12">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
        <div class="h-px w-12 bg-primary"></div>
        <p class="font-body-lg text-[length:var(--text-body-lg)] text-on-surface-variant max-w-md">
          Elevamos marcas a través de soluciones de ingeniería precisas y diseño minimalista. No solo construimos sitios, orquestamos experiencias digitales de alto rendimiento.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex justify-end items-end">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-6xl animate-bounce">arrow_downward</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
